casebody.data:
Kaitlin HAHN, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
GEICO INDEMNITY COMPANY, Defendant-Appellant,
and
Automobile Club Insurance Association, Defendant. SC: 158141(58)
COA: 336583 Supreme Court of Michigan. February 14, 2019

Order

On order of the Chief Justice, the motion of the Insurance Alliance of Michigan to file an untimely brief amicus curiae is GRANTED. The amicus brief submitted on February 1, 2019, is accepted for filing.
